OL,3,CForgotten no more: Growing demand for
OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Journalist in New
OL,7,FDelhi, Sanjay Jha
OL,9,FMore than 2.5 million Indian soldiers
OL,10,Fserved in the Allied forces during
OL,11,FSecond World War - forming the largest
OL,12,Fvolunteer army in history.
OL,14,FFrom the deserts of North Africa to
OL,15,Fthe mountains of Italy and the jungles
OL,16,Fof Burma, they fought with courage and
OL,17,Fdistinction. Yet, their sacrifice
OL,18,Fremains largely overlooked, both in
OL,19,FIndia and abroad.
