OL,3,CForgotten no more: Growing demand for
OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,F"It is unfortunate that there is no
OL,7,Fdedicated memorial to the Indian Army
OL,8,Fin World War Two - neither in India
OL,9,Fnor in the UK. If such a memorial were
OL,10,Fto come up, it would be a very welcome
OL,11,Fstep," he told ITV News.
OL,13,FChhina also highlighted the complexity
OL,14,Fof India's wartime role. The British
OL,15,FViceroy unilaterally declared war on
OL,16,FGermany in 1939 without consulting
OL,17,FIndia's elected leaders.
