OL,6,FWhile many Indian political parties
OL,7,Fopposed fascism, they demanded
OL,8,Findependence in return for supporting
OL,9,Fthe war effort - a demand Britain
OL,10,Frefused. Yet, millions still
OL,11,Fvolunteered.
OL,13,F"The Indian story in World War Two is
OL,14,Fslightly more complicated," Chhina
OL,15,Fsaid to ITV News.
