OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,F"The Viceroy declared war without
OL,7,Fconsulting political leadership. While
OL,8,FIndian leaders opposed fascism, they
OL,9,Fbelieved a nation fighting for
OL,10,Fdemocracy abroad deserved its own
OL,11,Ffreedom."
OL,13,FDespite these tensions, Indian
OL,14,Fsoldiers served with honour in nearly
OL,15,Fevery major theatre of the war.
OL,17,FMandeep Singh Bajwa, Military Affairs
OL,18,FColumnist at The Indian Express,
OL,19,Fechoed this sentiment.
