OL,3,CForgotten no more: Growing demand for
OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,F"A total of four million Indians
OL,7,Ffought on the Allied side in both
OL,8,Fworld wars. 176,000 gave up their
OL,9,Flives. The country's contribution in
OL,10,Fterms of manpower, goods, and money
OL,11,Fwas phenomenal," he told ITV News.
OL,13,F"But very few people in Europe or
OL,14,FAmerica know this. It's high time a
OL,15,Fmagnificent monument is built in
OL,16,FBritain to commemorate those who
OL,17,Ffought, and the governments of India,
OL,18,FPakistan, and Bangladesh should all be
OL,19,Finvolved in its unveiling."
