OL,3,CForgotten no more: Growing demand for
OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,FMomentum for such a memorial has grown
OL,7,Fsince British artist Mahtab Hussain
OL,8,Flaunched a petition on Change.org
OL,9,Fcalling for recognition of Indian
OL,10,Fsoldiers' wartime service.
OL,12,F"The Indian soldiers who fought in
OL,13,FWorld War Two have been forgotten for
OL,14,Ftoo long," Hussain wrote in the appeal.
OL,16,F"Their stories, their bravery, their
OL,17,Fsacrifice - they deserve a permanent
OL,18,Fmemorial that acknowledges their
OL,19,Funique contribution, especially here
OL,20,Fin London."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
