OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,FWhile the Cenotaph and the Memorial
OL,7,FGates on Constitution Hill acknowledge
OL,8,FCommonwealth contributions, critics
OL,9,Fargue they fail to reflect the scale
OL,10,Fand specificity of India's role in the
OL,11,Fwar.
OL,13,FIndia's own record of remembrance is
OL,14,Fsimilarly lacking. Journalist Sudhir
OL,15,FArora of the Garhwal Post has
OL,16,Fquestioned why India continues to
OL,17,Fsideline its Second World War veterans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
