OL,6,FThere was reluctance to honour a
OL,7,Fmilitary effort seen as part of
OL,8,FBritish imperialism. But that
OL,9,Fnarrative, critics argue, misses the
OL,10,Fbroader point: Indian soldiers also
OL,11,Ffought against fascism.
OL,13,FTheir sacrifice, they say, is not just
OL,14,Fa British or colonial story - it's an
OL,15,FIndian one.
