OL,3,CForgotten no more: Growing demand for
OL,4,CUK memorial to India's WW2 Heroes
OL,6,FAlthough India inaugurated a National
OL,7,FWar Memorial in 2019, it honours only
OL,8,Fpost-independence martyrs. The graves
OL,9,Fof Indian World War Two soldiers,
OL,10,Fmaintained by the Commonwealth War
OL,11,FGraves Commission at the Delhi War
OL,12,FCemetery, remain largely forgotten and
OL,13,Frarely visited.
OL,15,FAs Chhina noted, remembrance must go
OL,16,Fbeyond mere physical structures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
